## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Purpose

Дҗбә·c tбәЈ chб»©c nДғng chi tiбәҝt cho SDLC Memory MCP Server skeleton вҖ” bao gб»“m dual-transport (stdio + HTTP), CLI configuration, vГ  MCP protocol handshake.

### 1.2 Scope

* Kotlin MCP Server vб»ӣi Gradle build system
* stdio JSON-RPC 2.0 transport cho Kiro agent communication
* Ktor HTTP server cho Web Viewer API
