## 2. System Overview

### 2.1 System Context Diagram

![System Context](data:image/png;base64...)

System Context

The SDLC Memory MCP Server operates as a standalone process with two communication interfaces: - **stdio**: Kiro IDE connects via process stdin/stdout using JSON-RPC 2.0 - **HTTP**: Web Viewer connects via HTTP REST API on configurable port

